<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٢ في <span class="c1">"ص"</span>: <span class="c1">"السترة"</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
